This repo is under my tcopeland account temporarily... soon we'll move it over to the rubycentral account and delete this repo.

This is a port of the RubyForge codebase to Rails.  It's about time!

Some plans:

we'll migrate existing data over; e.g., we're not tied to current rubyforge schema
TOM: post up a sanitized data dump
- set all passwords to Digest::MD5.hexdigest("password") # <= 5f4dcc3b5aa765d61d8327deb882cf99
- normalize all emails to user_1@example.org
What domain data will we keep? (see table listing further down)
- User
- Membership
- Group
- Project


